            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-07-17T23:59:59-04:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-01-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="147" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d147">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Department of State, in an exchange of communications with Denmark, Italy,
                    and Norway between April 5 and 7, 1949, agreed to extend military assistance to
                    these nations in keeping with the principle of self-help and mutual aid agreed
                    upon in the North Atlantic Treaty. These communications are printed in the
                    Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, April 17, 1949, pages
                    495–498.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
